content: Enjoy terrifying unsuspecting folks by dressing up as your favorite deceased homeowners with the Beetlejuice Maitland masks. Each mask is made from lightweight foam and comes with black fabric over the eyes so you can see and move around with ease.

Transform yourself into your favorite power-absorbing mutant by dressing up in the X-Men Rogue costume. It’s made from Lycra so it contours perfectly to your body and comes designed just like Rogue’s iconic suit from the comic books and cartoons.

Give your outfit a touch of color and youthful appeal by toting around the LEGO brick purse. The vibrant design is composed entirely out of LEGO bricks that will set you apart from the fashion lemmings sporting conventional bags.

Spark your young genius’s curiosity in the science of the cosmos from a young age by entertaining them with the solar system planets baby mobile. The colorful design captivates your baby’s attention to keep them entertained and quiet.

Terrify neighbors, solicitors, and other scoundrels who dare approach your home with the metal alien sculpture placed in your front yard. This work of art takes discarded metal and gives it new life in the form of this incredible movie inspired statue.

Set your family apart from the rest by immortalizing your likeness by ordering the custom LEGO portrait. Each stunning portrait is skillfully put together utilizing only LEGO bricks to create a unique mosaic that perfectly captures you and your loved ones.

Enjoy the company of a furry little friend while you sew away with the pushpin hedgehog by your side. This little guy is handmade using upcycled wool and is designed so that the more pins and needles you add, the more he takes the shape of a hedgehog.

Fight for control of the Earthrealm by dressing up as one of your favorite Mortal Kombat characters with these hand tailored costumes. The costumes are available in a variety of character styles – from icons like Scorpion to obscure fighters like Noob Saibot.

Turn your little space explorer’s room into ground zero for intergalactic adventures with this spaceship fold up bed. During the day the bed conveniently folds up to provide more room for activities and at night it lowers so he can blast off into dreamland.

Start your night of bad decision making on the right note by paying homage to the party gods with a short prayer in front of the realistic Jagermeister logo sign. This altar of alcohol brings the iconic Jager logo to life while giving the room a lovely puke green glow.

Beef up your home’s security and ward off burglars and solicitors by enlisting the services of the recycled metal Bumblebee statue. Standing over six feet tall, it towers over most human peasants and is intricately designed with dozens of discarded scrap metal parts.

Stand out at the next festival or rave you attend by going dressed in the fiber optic tank top. When the lights go off, this unique garment comes alive with enough ultra bright rainbow color changing LEDs to turn you into a human glowstick.

Add a touch of brilliant blue to your rocking crystal collection with this chalcanthite mineral specimen. This beauty comes direct from recent dig sites in Arizona and displays a combination of earth tones with striking light blue accents.

Let your children stroll the blocky streets of LEGOville in style when they show up wearing one of these LEGO costumes. With these handmade costumes, they’ll be able to transform themselves into their favorite character from the LEGO movie like Benny or Emit.

Amplify your movie watching experience with an overload of flavor by snacking on some bacon caramel and cheddar popcorn. One mouthful of this buttery, cheesy, and caramely treat and you’ll never again want to go back to the cheap stuff.

Experience first hand what a mouth full of Uranus tastes like by indulging in a savory planetary lollipop. These custom treats come individually packaged to ensure freshness and are each emblazoned with a detailed rendition of a planet from our solar system.

Put a stop to the endless solicitors and Jehovah’s witnesses knocking at your door when you strategically place a few buried skull garden decorations along your front yard. They come expertly designed to look just like a real human skull, making it ideal for pranks.

Introduce a piece of your glorious 90s childhood into your adult life by keeping warm with the Reptar hoodie. Styled like your favorite misunderstood giant reptile, this all-green sweater features a comfy fit and Reptar’s iconic scales along the backside.

The Tetris water nail decals are the ultimate way to add a geeky flair to your plain manicure. With 36 colorful Tetris decals at your disposal, you’ll be able to create all kinds of different scenarios so that each nail has its own unique design.

Create amazing visual effects as you wow spectators with the strobe LED hula hoop. Ideal for performers and fun seekers alike, it features a blend of 24 strategically placed colored strobing LEDs working in unison to take your routine to new heights.

Relive all the glorious memories of gaming days gone by playing on the transparent Nintendo Game Boy. This rare find comes in perfect working condition in addition to including a vintage copy of Tetris in its original packaging.

Take a trip back in time by transforming yourself into a virtuous warrior when you suit up in the medieval knight armor. Inspired by the fearless warriors of the 16th century, these one of a kind suits can be worn or displayed in your home for all to marvel at.

Give your living room a quirky touch that’ll satisfy your inner child without sacrificing your home’s grown-up, decor with the LEGO brick coffee table. Styled like a ginormous LEGO brick, its unique design makes it a perfect fit for any room in your humble abode.

Let your favorite Pokemon keep you warm and looking incredibly stylish with the Pikachu hoodie. This extremely soft and adorable garment is made with no-pill fleece and felt accents that transform your torso into everyone’s favorite electric rodent.

Become the undisputed king of the attention whores when you show up donning this sound activated top hat. Once the tunes start bumping the eye catching hat comes alive as the vibrant LED strips light up and pulsate to the rhythm of the night.

Give your alternative history cosplay getup the ideal complementary weapon by arming yourself with the steampunk NERF gun. The gun comes expertly crafted to look like rusted metal while the intricate detailing and accents like tattered leather make it ideal for cosplay.

titleEN: Nintendo Game Boy Light Switch Cover
content: Give your room’s drab decor a bit of gamer flair with the Nintendo Game Boy light switch cover. Styled like an old school Game Boy, this custom cover is designed to fit most switches and even comes with specially painted screws to match the unique color scheme.

Join the elite ranks of the Empire’s oppressive army when you don the Star Wars stormtrooper helmet. This handmade replica is made with high quality resin, fiberglass, and is accented with vinyl graphics to achieve a cinema-grade appearance.

Consume a month’s worth of grease and cholesterol in one sitting by dining on the orgasmic chocolate covered bacon. Each thick and juicy slab of prime hickory smoked bacon comes drenched in savory chocolate for the ultimate artery clogging treat.

Shut up and take my hand in marriage! Upon opening the Zelda rupee engagement ring box, hearing the iconic sound, and seeing a fabulous ring concealed inside this over sized rupee there’s no way your geeky princess will ever turn down your proposal.

Give any room in your home an intriguing nautical edge by hanging a few of these wall tentacles. Life’s too short for timid decor – this vivid and expertly crafted tentacle protrudes from the wall to create and eye-catching conversation piece for the room.

Help vanquish the forces of evil by morphing yourself into a fearless fighter with the Xena Warrior Princess cosplay outfit. This tailored costume is crafted from lightweight yet durable materials that have been treated to achieve maximum authenticity.

Create a far-out psychedelic environment without the use of illicit substances by this unique mood setting light. The light bulb comes adorned with an abstract and colorful design that projects an eye-catching array of groovy colors and patterns onto the walls.

Hangout with all your old video game buddies every night when you snuggle up with one of these custom character quilts. These quilts comes in either a cotton or flannel fabric finish while showcasing a classic video game character in all their 8-bit glory.

Lull your offspring into a deep slumber by creating a serene environment with the cloud nightlight. The cloud is available in 3 distinct sizes and emits a dim white glow bright enough to be able to move around without turning on all the lights and waking up the kids.

Fight against cold weather and the Foot Clan simultaneously with these Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles beanies. They come available in a variety styles like Leonardo, Donatello, Rafael, or Michelangelo – so you can choose your favorite turtle.

Give your room an eerie touch when you summon the deep sea angler fish statue from the depths to provide some ambient lighting. This statue perfectly captures the angler fish’s terrifying appearance while his beady eyes and hanging lantern provide a spooky glow.

Guarantee your survival when you head into the chaotic streets with the zombie slayer axe in hand. If the razor sharp axe head doesn’t get them the first time around, the spiked brass knuckles built into the handle will surely finish the job.

Clean up the streets by suiting up in the Batman full armor set. Tailored specifically to your body measurements for maximum comfort and mobility, this menacing crimefighter’s suit features a slew of all black body armor plates for ultimate protection.

Help shorten the time it takes to find your luggage in those crowed baggage terminals by attaching a shout my name luggage tag. Once the bright colors draw the eyes, the clever printed message will entice a fellow traveler to shout your name so you can find your bag.

Transform yourself into a royal family member of Hyrule with this intricately designed Zelda cosplay outfit. The dress is handmade with extreme attention to detail so that you can convincingly pull off the look. Shut up and take my rupees!

Throw caution to the wind and live a little by embracing the mantra printed on the life motto pillows. Life’s too short to be constantly stressing, so indulge in life’s ultimate pleasures – like delicious fried pork and exhilarating cardiovascular workouts with a partner.

Keep your gorgeous mug looking as beautiful as ever by walking into battle wearing the Street Fighter Vega mask. This handmade mask is cast in high impact resin while the raised symbol is sealed for durability, making it a fantastic cosplay accessory.

titleEN: In Case Of Zombies Wall Decal
content: Keep your <del>weapons</del> garden tools organized and accessible at a moments notice by labeling them using the “In Case Of Zombies” wall decal. It’s the perfect way to keep your tools handy for when there are zombies to slay or chores to complete.

Ascend to the ranks of basketball’s elite when you hit the courts wearing the Space Jam Tune Squad jersey. Worn by the likes of Jordan, Bugs Bunny, and Bill Murray, this gem sports the classic logo and design, making it an ideal collectible for any 90s afficionado.

Keep your tiny barbarian warm while looking adorable in this lovely baby viking hat. This cute hand knit garment is made in the likeness of a classic viking helmet – complete with two tiny horns – and accents around the rim.

Give your outfit a futuristic antiquey touch with the steampunk wrap earring. This lovely accessory is made from vintage watch parts, brass, and copper wire and features a design that doesn’t require you to have your ears pierced in order to wear it.

Enjoy a splash of nostalgia in every shower you take by scrubbing yourself clean with the Super Nintendo soap bars. Each bar is made in the likeness of the original game cartridges and controllers, right down to the smallest detail.

Keep all the backyard ornaments in check by having the Dexter garden gnome move into the neighborhood. Skillfully painted with attention to detail, this loveable serial killer stares at you with his souless eyes as he leans over his blood soaked victim.

Morph yourself into the mightiest Power Ranger of them all with this Green Power Ranger costume. Made with superb attention to detail, it will help you embody the fearless pony-tailed leader. Dragonzord summoning dagger sold separately.

All lives matter – not just your bratty kids – so let the world know of your desire to live another day with the “Adults On Board” car sticker. This informative bumper sticker lets fellow drivers know to drive with caution around you – because you too were once a child.

Get the face tattoo you’ve always wanted without fear of being fired from your job with these temporary eye tattoos. Ideal for masquerade parties or adding some extra flair to your night time look, each tattoo features an intricate and equally beautiful design.

Immortalize one of cinema’s most iconic scenes with The Exorcist amigurumi set. This hand crocheted item masterfully captures young Reagan sitting atop her bed as she projectile vomits all over the stunned and bewildered Father Merrin.

Power up your room’s decor by illuminating it using the NES zapper gun lamp. This nostalgic lamp is custom made using the iconic orange and grey Nintendo gun as the shaft and the original controller as the base – ideal for adding a little geeky flair to any room.

When you’re not sure what to top off your outfit with, the Star Wars themed R2-D2 purse is the <del>droid</del> accessory you’ve been looking for. Made from fine wool felt, it’s decorated with detailed prints and embroideries to achieve an authentic look.

Give your curious children yet another reason to play with the wall socket by adhering these electrical outlet face stickers. These vinyl stickers are placed over plain outlets, transforming them into comical characters that the tiny tots will be dying to play with.

Enjoy the tastiest slice of your life without gaining a single pound with these trendy pizza leggings. They fit like a greasy glove and come emblazoned with a vivid and deliciously detailed graphic of cheesy pepperoni pizza slices.

Relive Mario’s illustrious accomplishments on a daily basis by decorating your home with a Super Mario print. Ideal for adding a splash of geeky flavor to any home, these custom prints feature a matte finish depicting the heroic Italian plumber’s adventures.

Reach for the confetti Oreos and experience a foodgasm the next time you’re craving something sweet. You’ll get to enjoy a dozen double stuffed Oreos completely drenched with a white chocolate coating and topped off with colorful sprinkles.

Revitalize yourself after a long day  of slashing grass and smashing pots by taking in the delicious scent of the Zelda Lon Lon milk candle. Styled after the iconic and savory drink from the video game series, these scented candles can burn for up to ten hours.

Take a cue from Tony Stark and shift all the attention towards yourself by walking into the room wearing the deluxe Iron Man costume. Featuring a movie quality level of detailing, it includes working lights in the hands and chest plate for added authenticity.

Let your gamer roots shine through by illuminating your home with Pac-Man stained glass lamp. This custom beauty employs the stained glass technique to bring you a unique and clever novelty lamp ideal for any game room.

Power up your mornings with a dose of caffeine by having your morning cup of Joe in the Nintendo Game Boy coffee cup. This ceramic mug’s nostalgic Nintendo theme makes it ideal for every gamer looking to charge up their batteries for the long day ahead.

While everyone you love is avoiding your disease ridden body, you can always count on the dinosaur tissue holder to be by your side. Simply place this vibrant dino over your existing tissue box and you’ve got a lovable friend there to lend some company.

Unleash the primitive beast inside by embodying it on the outside with the Predator cosplay costume. This movie quality ensemble features intricate artistic detailing and includes all the accessories needed to become the ultimate hunter.

Let it go! Let it go! And by “it” – we mean your figure, by indulging in some treats accented with these Frozen cupcake toppers. Ideal for birthdays and other celebrations, these custom toppers feature a detailed rendition of Elsa that your little princess will love.

Upgrade those pathetic noodles you call arms with the steampunk robot arm gauntlets. These intricately detailed gloves features a combination of leather, brass, rivets, and buckles to achieve an extraordinarily realistic look.

Increase your chances of staying alive in the wild by taking along the Altoid tin survival kit. The compact kit fits virtually anywhere and comes jam packed with all the essential tools – like an emergency whistle, fishing wire, and a button compass.

Show off your unique fashion sense when you strut the streets wearing the sugar and spice heelless wedges. Styled like Lisa Frank vomited onto a blank canvas – the shoes contain a plethora of pink, pastel, and just about anything girly you can imagine.

Let your significant other know that you choose them to embark on life’s greatest journey by throwing a Pokemon engagement ring box at their heads. After they get over the anger, they’ll have no choice by to say yes after peaking at the goods inside.

Let your geeky roots show through by greeting incoming guests with the RPG menu doormat. This novelty doormat comes decorated with stunning 16-bit graphics that allow your guests to choose 1 of 4 options when they arrive at your humble abode.

Keep track of your little one’s height throughout the years with the growth chart ruler decal. This giant ruler stretches stretches up to seventy four inches and displays the height in both inches and centimeters so your child can learn the value of the metric system.

Keep your hands nice and toasty like a true Marvel fan with these one of a kind Iron Man hand warmers. Each skillfully crocheted hand warmer comes accented with blue yarn blasters in each palm and features thumb holes to allow for maximum practicality.

Place the finishing touch on your post-apocalyptic outfit with this distinguished steampunk torso armor. This handmade vest comes laden with a plethora of leather, rivets, buckles, brass, and gears to ensure you’re ready for any battle that comes your way.

Ready yourself for some interstellar bounty hunting like a true gamer by equipping yourself with the Metroid Samus helmet. This replica game prop fits most adult sized heads and features intricate detailing for added realism, making this an excellent gift for any gamer.

titleEN: The Fifth Element Multipass ID Holder
content: Carry around your identification in true 23rd century fashion when you acquire the Fifth Element multipass ID holder. Inspired by the cult classic, the ID holder is perfect for claiming a Gemini Croquette contest prize or trying to board a trans-system shuttle.

Stay ahead of the fashion curve by embracing the trends of the future by wearing the chrome cyborg corset. This handmade corset comes fully decked out with a robotic inspired motif ideal for putting together the quintessential sci-fi outfit.

Proclaim yourself queen of the dance floor when you show up wearing the eye catching metallic Cleopatra wig. The chic wig sports a classic Cleopatra hairstyle formed from insanely bright chrome strands that’ll turn you into the focus point of any room.

Get one step closer to fulfilling your childhood fantasy of morphing into an action hero with the Power Rangers helmet. Expertly cast in resin, the helmet perfectly captures every detail of the now iconic original series Power Rangers.

Stop waiting for expensive limited edition pieces for your ever-growing toy collection and opt for these handmade LEGO figurines. Whether you’re in the market for tertiary Simpsons characters or lesser known superheroes, this shop has them all.

Shut up and take my rupees! This deluxe cold cast polyurethane reinforced with fiberglass shield is fashioned after the Skyward Sword style with life like scale and a convex shape for a realistic appearance – making it ideal for cosplayers.

Let your little tike’s imagination soar when you let them fulfill their fantasies with these children’s superhero capes. No matter what super-powered being they idolize, there’s a pint-sized cape waiting to join them on countless crime fighting adventures.

content: Now you and your friends can make up countless creative scenarios and keep the laughs coming all day long as you watch the Caped Crusader slap that little bitch ass Robin for his idiotic remarks with the Batman slap meme dry erase board.
